collection referred to as "The

00:14:23.120 --> 00:14:25.890 align:middle line:90%
Seth Material."

00:14:25.890 --> 00:14:28.670 align:middle line:84%
>> The first time I heard about
the idea of channeling was when

00:14:28.670 --> 00:14:31.760 align:middle line:84%
