nomenclature of the New Age

00:14:36.890 --> 00:14:38.090 align:middle line:90%
movement.

00:14:38.090 --> 00:14:41.750 align:middle line:84%
>> When I was a kid, one of my
mom's favorite books was "Seth

00:14:41.750 --> 00:14:42.980 align:middle line:90%
Speaks."

00:14:42.980 --> 00:14:45.620 align:middle line:84%
Seth is a higher
level spirit that

00:14:45.620 --> 00:14:48.560 align:middle line:84%
