00:14:59.600 --> 00:15:02.180 align:middle line:84%
I should do what everyone else
does, grab the Ouija board.

00:15:02.180 --> 00:15:03.080 align:middle line:90%
And that worked.

00:15:03.080 --> 00:15:04.280 align:middle line:90%
That worked for a while.

00:15:04.280 --> 00:15:06.980 align:middle line:84%
But then she realized she
was more of a mental medium

00:15:06.980 --> 00:15:10.460 align:middle line:84%
