00:15:44.450 --> 00:15:45.920 align:middle line:10%
or anything.

00:15:45.920 --> 00:15:48.860 align:middle line:10%
But the thing of it was that
the stuff that was in the script

00:15:48.860 --> 00:15:52.250 align:middle line:10%
was stuff I had felt
while I was out.

00:15:52.250 --> 00:15:57.530 align:middle line:10%
But when I was out, I would
go into atoms and molecules.

00:15:57.530 --> 00:15:59.570 align:middle line:10%
And I felt their consciousness.

00:15:59.570 --> 00:16:02.090 align:middle line:10%
But then, when I
