00:16:25.490 --> 00:16:28.370 align:middle line:84%
ways to make that reality
conform to our belief and that

00:16:28.370 --> 00:16:29.840 align:middle line:90%
we create that.

00:16:29.840 --> 00:16:31.610 align:middle line:90%
And my mom loved these books.

00:16:31.610 --> 00:16:33.478 align:middle line:84%
She talked about
Seth all the time.

00:16:33.478 --> 00:16:35.270 align:middle line:84%
And I think that was
one of the things that

00:16:35.270 --> 00:16:37.730 align:middle line:84%
