00:16:47.390 --> 00:16:50.210 align:middle line:84%
Simply just by knowing
this information

00:16:50.210 --> 00:16:52.880 align:middle line:90%
helped her out dramatically.

00:16:52.880 --> 00:16:57.620 align:middle line:10%
>> People, you might use them
or think of them as symbols.

00:16:57.620 --> 00:16:59.510 align:middle line:10%
Or no matter how
