00:17:18.470 --> 00:17:20.790 align:middle line:10%
It will bring you
closer to people.

00:17:20.790 --> 00:17:22.895 align:middle line:10%
It will not divide you.

00:17:22.895 --> 00:17:26.300 align:middle line:10%
If it divides you,
