00:18:00.410 --> 00:18:04.310 align:middle line:84%
at the essence of these
philosophical teachings

00:18:04.310 --> 00:18:05.850 align:middle line:90%
and so forth.

00:18:05.850 --> 00:18:07.760 align:middle line:84%
And that was thrilling
