00:18:07.760 --> 00:18:10.190 align:middle line:84%
think it's important for
people, and especially women,

00:18:10.190 --> 00:18:12.770 align:middle line:84%
to feel like they
can be bringing forth

00:18:12.770 --> 00:18:17.880 align:middle line:84%
this high-level philosophical
