some white cloaked spirit

00:19:22.210 --> 00:19:24.580 align:middle line:10%
who was just floating around.

00:19:24.580 --> 00:19:26.530 align:middle line:10%
Part of my life's
work certainly is

00:19:26.530 --> 00:19:30.250 align:middle line:10%
to try to understand the
nature of our personalities,

00:19:30.250 --> 00:19:33.820 align:middle line:10%
our personalities, what
abilities we've got,

00:19:33.820 --> 00:19:38.660 align:middle line:10%
what happens so that we can
get this kind of information.

00:19:38.660 --> 00:19:41.500 align:middle line:10%
And one of the things
that I really hope

00:19:41.500 --> 00:19:45.580 align:middle line:10%
is that people would begin
to trust their own revelatory

00:19:45.580 --> 00:19:50.290 align:middle line:10%
experience and not automatically
cloak it in whatever dogma

00:19:50.290 --> 00:19:51.820 align:middle line:10%
they believe in.

00:19:51.820 --> 00:19:55.420 align:middle line:84%
>> Jane Roberts, I think,
was really someone who opened

00:19:55.420 --> 00:19:58.060 align:middle line:84%
the door for a lot of people
to know that they could

00:19:58.060 --> 00:20:00.970 align:middle line:84%
investigate these things,
that there are some profound

00:20:00.970 --> 00:20:05.020 align:middle line:84%
differences in states of beings
