00:20:13.630 --> 00:20:16.840 align:middle line:10%
from almost anything else that
was out there at the time.

00:20:16.840 --> 00:20:18.310 align:middle line:84%
I think she's
generally considered

00:20:18.310 --> 00:20:22.810 align:middle line:84%
