00:20:32.500 --> 00:20:35.603 align:middle line:10%
She was very, in a sense,
irreverent about it,

00:20:35.603 --> 00:20:36.520 align:middle line:10%
which was interesting.

00:20:36.520 --> 00:20:37.683 align:middle line:10%
Because I know she smoked.

00:20:37.683 --> 00:20:39.100 align:middle line:10%
I know she drank
