00:20:39.100 --> 00:20:41.410 align:middle line:10%
channeled to loosen herself up.

00:20:41.410 --> 00:20:43.420 align:middle line:10%
And different people
have different ways

00:20:43.420 --> 00:20:44.960 align:middle line:10%
of getting into that state.

00:20:44.960 --> 00:20:47.230 align:middle line:10%
And if she felt she
needed to just lose

00:20:47.230 --> 00:20:49.450 align:middle line:10%
a little bit of her
inhibitions to do so,

00:20:49.450 --> 00:20:52.090 align:middle line:10%
well, then that's
what worked for her.

00:20:52.090 --> 00:20:57.220 align:middle line:84%
But I think that the fundaments
of "The Seth Material,"

00:20:57.220 --> 00:21:00.310 align:middle line:84%
the core information in
"The Seth Material," I think

00:21:00.310 --> 00:21:05.620 align:middle line:84%
you'll find that in almost any
channel now, because it really,

00:21:05.620 --> 00:21:07.840 align:middle line:84%
for the first time, I think,
